# Weekly Structure

Each week follows the same workflow.

1. Study
2. Research
3. Design
4. Implement
5. Test
6. Benchmark
7. Deploy
8. Document
9. Review
10. Reflect

---

# Deliverables

Every week produces:

- Working software
- Tests
- Documentation
- ADRs
- Benchmarks
- Diagrams
- Pull Requests

